firstPurchase.text:
Welcome to Future Fortune! Purchase your first resource, 
    Fire, to begin production in the Survival industry.

firstUpgrade.text:
Resources can be upgraded every time you purchase 10 of them. 
    Resource upgrades provide a 2x production boost!

milestonesOpened.text:
Open the milestones panel to check your progress towards earning
    booster rewards that boost your progress!

boostersOpened.text:
Open the boosters panel to view all the amazing boosters you have
    earned from completing milestones.

ascensionOpened.text:
Open the ascension panel to view all the amazing upgrades you can purchase
    with your hard earned ascension points.

rebirthOpened.text:
Open the rebirth panel to view all the amazing upgrades you can purchase
    with your powerful rebirth points.

promotionsOpened.text: Open the promotions panel to view all the resource promotions you've earned!

pr.text:
Oh look, your first prestige! Prestiging industries gives a boost to
    production and speed of resources in that industry. You should prestige now.

in.text:
Innovation, how neat! Innovating unlocks new industries and new resources
    to enhance production. Innovations grant a boost to production and speed of
    all unlocked industries!

as.text:
Making good progress I see. Ascension unlocks powerful upgrades that can
    be purchased with Ascension Points. You should ascend right away because the
    first ascension is capped at 1 AP!

re.text:
Wow, rebirth! You should definitely check this out, there are some very
    powerful upgrades that you can purchase with rebirth points. The first
    rebirth is capped at 1 RP, so rebirth as soon as you're ready!

au.text: Open the automation panel to enable, disable, and monitor your automation.

rdW.text:
The reward wheel allows you to spin to earn magnificient rewards! Open it
    now to start your first spin.
